OL,5,BUsing the edit server                  
OL,7,BChunkytext uses theEBlock Party editing
OL,8,EserverBcreated by ZXGuesser.           
OL,10,BIt enables anyone to create and edit   
OL,11,Bgenuine teletext pages for display on  
OL,12,Beither the zxnet.co.ukEonline viewerBor
OL,13,BaEreal teletext TV.C                   
OL,15,BTo get started, point your web browser 
OL,16,BatEblockparty.zxnet.co.uk              
