OL,5,BSelecting a teletext editor            
OL,7,BThe edit server contains specially     
OL,8,Bmodified versions of the two popular   
OL,9,Bonline teletext editors,Eedit.tfBand   
OL,10,BtheEzxnet editor.                      
OL,12,BThe rest of this guide is written for  
OL,13,Bthe latter, but the same principles    
OL,14,Bapply to both.                         
OL,16,BSelect zxnet from the main page, which 
OL,17,Bwill start load the editor with aEblank
OL,18,Epage.B                                 
