OL,5,BUploading your page to Chunkytext      
OL,7,BOnce you've mastered teletext editing, 
OL,8,Bclick theEsave this pageBbutton in the 
OL,9,Bpage server interface box. This stores 
OL,10,Byour page in the system and adds it to 
OL,11,Bthe Chunkytext service.                
OL,13,BThe server automatically assigns aEnew 
OL,14,Epage number.BIf you decide you want to 
OL,15,Bchange something on your page you can  
OL,16,Benter the number and clickEload a page.
OL,18,BSaving again willEoverwriteBthe page   
OL,19,Bunless the save as new box is checked  
OL,20,E``````````````````````````````````4/5``
OL,21,       BThe ghost of Digi pastE170      
OL,22,D]MGTRY BRIAN'S VINTAGE SPORT QUIZ p151 
OL,24,AAbout BMicroBrits BookCDigitiser FIndex
