OL,5,BUploading your page to Chunkytext      
OL,7,BYou can load most of the pages on this 
OL,8,Bservice into the editor to see how they
OL,9,Bare constructed, or use as a template  
OL,10,Bfor your own creations.                
OL,12,BThe editor is unable to load or save   
OL,13,Ecarousel pagesBlike this one, so will  
OL,14,Bshow the first subpage only.           
OL,16,BPlease don't edit other people's pages 
OL,17,Bwithout permission. AnyEvandalismBcan  
OL,18,Bbe reverted, just tweet @ZXGuesser.    
OL,20,E``````````````````````````````````5/5``
OL,21,  BThese kids are in their 30s nowE147  
OL,22,D]MGSPECCY AND SINCLAIR C5 OH MY! p120  
OL,24,AAbout BMicroBrits BookCDigitiser FIndex
